steps.name: Given User has already Logged in
Given The user is on the "NumpyNinja" Home Page
When User clicks on Get Started button index 3
Then User should be on "Stack" page
Given User is on the "Stack" Home Page of URL "https://dsportalapp.herokuapp.com/stack/"
Then User should navigate to page that contains title 'Applications'
When User clicks Try Here button of "Applications"
And The user is on the "Assessment" Home Page
When The user write code in Editor from sheetname 'pythonCode' and rownumber 0
Then The user should able to see output in the console "hello"
And The user is on the "Assessment" Home Page
When The user write code in Editor from sheetname 'pythonCode' and rownumber 1
Then The user should able to see an error message in alert window
And The user is on the "Assessment" Home Page
